<% content_for :title, "About" %>

<!-- start of page-header -->
<section class="page-header bg-light-gray has-shapes has-bg-brash bg-brash-bottom" style="background-image: url(<%= image_path "banner.svg" %>)">
  <div class="container h-100">
    <div class="row d-flex align-items-center h-100">
      <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
        <h2 class="h1 font-weight-bold">About</h2>
        <nav class="mt-15" aria-label="breadcrumb">
          <ol class="breadcrumb font-weight-bold bg-transparent p-0 justify-content-center">
            <li class="breadcrumb-item"><%= link_to "Home", root_path, class: "text-black-300" %></li>
            <li class="breadcrumb-item text-primary" aria-current="page">About</li>
          </ol>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="shape-1 bg-secondary shape-xs rounded-circle"></div>
  <div class="shape-2 bg-primary shape-xs-2 rounded-circle"></div>
  <div class="shape-3 bg-primary shape-sm-2 rounded-circle"></div>
  <div class="shape-4 bg-tertiary shape-xs rounded-circle"></div>
  <div class="shape-5 bg-tertiary shape-xs rounded-circle"></div>
  <div class="shape-6 bg-primary shape-sm rounded-circle"></div>
  <div class="shape-7 bg-primary shape-xs-2 rounded-circle"></div>
  <div class="shape-8 bg-secondary shape-xs rounded-circle"></div>
</section>


<!-- start section -->
<section class="section-padding" data-aos="fade-in" data-aos-delay="150">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row align-items-center justify-content-around">
      <div class="col-lg-5 col-md-8 col-sm-10 mb-5">
        <h3 class="section-title">
          The mission - <br>
          <strong style="text-transform: uppercase !important;">
            Help entrepreneurs start, nurture and grow  sustainable businesses.
          </strong>
        </h3>
        <p class="pb-20 border-bottom mb-20">
          We see projects and businesses starting up here and there 
          in Africa, only to disappear quickly due to poor business planning and lack of 
          funds. Those that are resilient enough soon become difficult to sustain over a 
          period of time. Most ultimately fail after 3 years! That's an enormouse waste 
          of time, energy and capital. <br>
          
          Without the right business tools, information, 
          adequate finances and funding, most of the projects that can change the 
          African narrative are rarely able to break out from being just an idea, 
          let alone grow into a tangible business.<br><br>

          <span style="font-weight: bold; color: gray; font-size: 18px;">
            This is the problem <strong class="text-primary">Brainstaq</strong> solves!
          </span>
        </p>
        
        <ul class="check-list list-unstyled">
          <li class="mb-15">
            <svg width="16" height="11" viewBox="0 0 18 13" class="text-primary mr-2" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M2 6.125L6.91892 11L16 2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            Build something!<br>
            Every idea and project has a fighting chance to grow and reach their true potential.
            Brainstaq harnesses your potentials to create the solutions of tomorrow.
          </li>
          <li class="mb-15">
            <svg width="16" height="11" viewBox="0 0 18 13" class="text-primary mr-2" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M2 6.125L6.91892 11L16 2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
              Brainstaq provide the tools to validate your business ideas and projects, 
              amplify your reach, enhance collaboration and helps you attract cofounders 
              and funding by engaging the power of the crowd.
          </li>
          <li class="mb-15">
            <svg width="16" height="11" viewBox="0 0 18 13" class="text-primary mr-2" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M2 6.125L6.91892 11L16 2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
              With Brainstaq you can create and manage your business plan, financial models, 
              and other documents, and make informed decisions in real-time.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-5 col-md-8 col-sm-10">
        <div class="d-inline-block has-shadow shadow-right has-shapes">
          <%= image_tag 'about-1.jpg', class: "img-fluid rounded-sm"%>

          <div class="shape-1 shape-md bg-secondary rounded-circle"></div>
          <div class="shape-2 shape-xl bg-tertiary rounded-circle"></div>
          <div class="shape-3 shape-lg bg-primary rounded-circle"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<!-- end section -->

<section class="pt-50 pb-50 mb-5 image-info-section bg-light-gray has-shapes bg-brash-bottom has-bg-brash bg-brash-y overflow-hidden">
  <%= render partial: "layouts/growth_rate" %>
</section>

<!-- start section -->
<section class="pt-120 pb-120 mb-5 image-info-section has-shapes bg-brash-bottom has-bg-brash bg-brash-y overflow-hidden">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row align-items-center justify-content-around">
      <div class="col-lg-5 col-md-8 col-sm-10">
        <div class="d-inline-block has-shadow shadow-left has-shapes">
          <%= image_tag 'goals.jpg', class: "img-fluid rounded-sm" %>

          <div class="shape-1 shape-md bg-secondary rounded-circle"></div>
          <div class="shape-2 shape-xl bg-tertiary rounded-circle"></div>
          <div class="shape-3 shape-lg bg-primary rounded-circle"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-5 col-md-8 col-sm-10 mt-5 mt-lg-0">
        <h2>Get on the ride. <br>
          <strong>We make it easier for entrepreneurs</strong>
        </h2>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="shape-3 shape-xs-2 bg-secondary rounded-circle"></div>
  <div class="shape-4 shape-sm-2 bg-tertiary rounded-circle"></div>
  <div class="shape-5 shape-sm bg-primary rounded-circle"></div>
  <div class="shape-6 shape-xs bg-secondary rounded-circle"></div>
  <div class="shape-7 shape-xs-2 bg-tertiary rounded-circle"></div>
</section>
<!-- end section -->


<style>
  .row {
    clear: both;
  }
</style>